<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Homepage</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="style.css">
</head>
<body><h1>FCC Timestamp Microservice</h1>
  <blockquote>
    <h3>User stories:</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>User Story:  I can pass a URL as a parameter and I will receive a shortened URL in the JSON response.
      </li>
      <li>User Story: If I pass an invalid URL that doesn't follow the valid http://www.example.com format, the JSON response will contain an error instead.
      </li>
      <li>User Story: When I visit that shortened URL, it will redirect me to my original link.
      </li>
    </ol>
  </blockquote>
  <h3>To shorten your URL:</h3>
  <code>http://<%= host %>/new/https://www.google.com</code><br>
  <code>http://<%= host %>/new/http://c9.io/dashboard</code>
  <h3>URL shortener output:</h3>
  <code>{"original": "https://www.google.com", "shortened": "http://<%=host%>/8712"}</code>
  <h3>To redirect to original URL:</h3>
  <code>https://<%= host %>/8712</code>
</body>
</html>
